name: oligopeptidase B
reaction: Hydrolysis of -Arg!, -Lys! bonds in oligopeptides, even when P1' residue is proline
comment: Known from Escherichia coli. Inhibited by Tos-Lys-CH2Cl. In peptidase family S9 (prolyl oligopeptidase family)

references.title: Protease II from Escherichia coli: sequencing and expression of the enzyme gene and characterization of the expressed enzyme.
